<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>About Us - Daftar Mobil</title>
    <style>
      /* Global Styles */
      body {
        font-family: "Arial", sans-serif;
        background-color: #f4f7fc;
        color: #333;
        line-height: 1.6;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
      }

      /* Header */
      header {
        background: linear-gradient(to right, #007bff, #00c6ff);
        color: white;
        text-align: center;
        padding: 30px 0;
        border-bottom-left-radius: 50%;
        border-bottom-right-radius: 50%;
      }

      header h1 {
        font-size: 3rem;
        letter-spacing: 1px;
        margin: 0;
        font-weight: 600;
      }

      /* Main Container */
      .container {
        max-width: 900px;
        margin: 30px auto;
        padding: 30px;
        background-color: white;
        box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        border-radius: 15px;
        text-align: center;
        transition: transform 0.3s ease;
      }

      .container:hover {
        transform: translateY(-5px);
      }

      .container h2 {
        font-size: 2rem;
        color: #333;
      }

      .container p {
        font-size: 1.1rem;
        color: #555;
        line-height: 1.8;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
      }

      /* Footer */
      footer {
        background-color: #333;
        color: white;
        text-align: center;
        padding: 20px 0;
        margin-top: 30px;
        border-top-left-radius: 50%;
        border-top-right-radius: 50%;
      }

      footer p {
        font-size: 1rem;
        margin: 0;
      }

      /* Button (Optional for "Contact Us" button) */
      .contact-btn {
        background-color: #007bff;
        color: white;
        padding: 12px 20px;
        border: none;
        border-radius: 25px;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        font-weight: bold;
        cursor: pointer;
        margin-top: 20px;
        transition: background-color 0.3s;
      }

      .contact-btn:hover {
        background-color: #0056b3;
      }
    </style>
  </head>

  <body>
    <!-- Header -->
    <header>
      <h1>About Us</h1>
    </header>

    <!-- Main Content -->
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Welcome to Daftar Mobil</h2>
      <p>
        Daftar Mobil is your trusted platform to find and explore a wide range
        of vehicles. We aim to make the car-buying process easier by offering
        detailed information, tips, and reviews on various car models. Whether
        you're looking for a family car, a sports car, or a used vehicle, we
        provide a comprehensive guide to help you make the right decision.
      </p>
      <p>
        Our team is passionate about cars and dedicated to providing useful,
        unbiased information to help you find the perfect vehicle. Thank you for
        visiting Daftar Mobil, and we hope you have a pleasant experience
        browsing our content!
      </p>

      <!-- Optional Button (e.g., "Contact Us") -->
      <a href="https://wa.me/6281234567890">
        <button class="contact-btn">Contact Us</button>
      </a>
    </div>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <footer>
      <p>&copy; 2025 Daftar Mobil. All rights reserved.</p>
    </footer>
  </body>
</html>
